relevant_findings.description: Secret outgoing message from CIA to Stockholm station
relevant_findings.direct_quote: WE HAVE BEGUN CHECKING WITH NOSENKO (PD)IPPERS 19 AND 20, AND (PD)ABLE RE WALLENBERG AND WILL CABLE OR TELEPOUCH RESULTS AS RECEIVED. WE EXPECT TO BE FINISHED BY MID-NOVEMBER-V
relevant_findings.significance: Indicates ongoing intelligence investigation related to Nosenko and Wallenberg, potentially connected to Cold War era intelligence gathering

relevant_findings.description: Reference to communication with Stockholm station suggests international intelligence coordination
relevant_findings.significance: Demonstrates cross-agency and international communication channels active during the time period
